bilingual.source: The young people were attracted by the legend of Loch Ness.
bilingual.target: 年轻人被尼斯湖的传说吸引。
诺亚方舟是一个古老的传说。

bilingual.source: Do you know the origin of this legend?
bilingual.target: 你知道这个传说的由来吗？

bilingual.source: The legend tells of a cursed king.
bilingual.target: 传说讲述了一位被诅咒的国王。

bilingual.source: According to legend, Kua Fu chased the sun.
In legend, the roc is a gigantic bird.
bilingual.target: 传说中，鲲鹏是一种巨大的鸟。

bilingual.source: There is an old legend in this village.
bilingual.target: 这个村子里有一个古老的传说。

bilingual.source: The legend has outlived the actual events.
bilingual.target: 这个传说比实际事件活得长。

bilingual.source: In the legend, the phoenix will come back to life.
Have you heard the legend of Seven Star Cave?
bilingual.target: 你听说过七星岩的传说吗？

list.abstract: 《黑道传奇》（Legend）是由布莱恩·海尔格兰德执导，布莱恩·海尔格兰德、约翰·皮尔逊担任编剧，汤姆·哈迪、艾米莉·布朗宁、大卫·休里斯等主演的一部惊悚电影，于2015年9月3日在英国上映。 该影片讲述了20世纪50到60年代，活跃在伦敦东区的犯罪团伙克雷孪生兄弟（汤姆·哈迪 饰）的故事。 2016年获得第42届土星奖最佳国际电影提名奖。 截至2022年11月，根据BOX Office Mojo官网显示，该片累计全球票房4297万美元。
《LEGEND》是由雷德利·斯科特执导，汤姆·克鲁斯、米娅·萨拉等主演的爱情奇幻冒险剧，片长达94分钟。影片讲述了大魔头“黑暗”准备将这个世界的光亮吞噬，使人类永远生活在黑暗中。森林小子杰克跟他的十一位好友决定联手对抗黑魔王，方法是杀死各地的独角兽。最后，杰克还赢得莉莉公主的芳心，打破了黑魔王迎娶公主的美梦。

yingyinNormal.en: Have you not heard the legend of the Shusher?
yingyinNormal.zh: 难道你没听说过关于嘘嘘的传说吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I was inspired by the legend of the Ant-Man.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但我被蚁人的传说激发了灵感。

yingyinNormal.en: Could that be done? Well, it's not a legend anymore.
yingyinNormal.zh: 究竟能不能做到？其实那已不再是传说。

yingyinNormal.en: Professor? What exactly does legend tell us lies within the Chamber?
yingyinNormal.zh: 麦格教授？传说有没有告诉我们密室中的东西是什么？
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: Now, according to legend, Slytherin had built a hidden chamber in this castle known as the Chamber of Secrets.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而根据传说呢，斯莱特林在城堡中建了一个隐藏的房间，大家都把这个房间称为密室。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: Right, games. They took Halo 1, Halo 2, Halo 3, Call of Duty 1, Call of Duty 2, Call of Duty 3, Rock Band, Rock Band 2, Final Fantasy 1 thru 9, the Legend of Zelda, The Legend of Zelda: ocarina of time, TheLegend of Zelda: twilight princess, Super Mario brothers, Super Mario galaxy, Mario and Sonic at the winter Olympics, and Ms. Pacman.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对，游戏，他们拿走了光晕1，光晕2，光晕3，使命召唤1，使命召唤2，使命召唤3，摇滚乐团，摇滚乐团2，最终幻想1到9，塞尔达传说，塞尔达传说之时光之笛，塞尔达传说之黎明公主，超级马里奥兄弟，超级马里奥银河，马里奥和索尼克在冬奥会，还有吃豆小姐。

yingyinNormal.en: According to legend, this secluded monastery is not only the birthplace of Zen Buddhism, here trained the legendary Shaolin monks.
yingyinNormal.zh: 传说，这个僻静的寺庙不仅是禅宗佛教的诞生地，这里培育了传奇的少林和尚。

yingyinNormal.en: It is especially important at New Year as Chinese legend has it that dragons are famed for bringing good luck to any new venture.
yingyinNormal.zh: 新年里，这很重要，因为在中国人的传说里，龙非常着名，它可以给任何新事业带来好运。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, this is a big thing. Most people, when they make bread, actually use warm water. It's a myth. It's a legend, and it's rubbish.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在是要注意的事情大多数人做面包时，通常使用温水，这是个神话，也是个传说，更是废话。

yingyinNormal.en: The chronosphere. The source that powers the grand clock of all time. Legend has, it also lets one travel across the ocean of time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 超时空魔球，据说它就是驱动世界上所有时间的动力源泉，传说通过它还能穿越古今，回到过去，进行时间旅行。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《爱丽丝梦游仙境2：镜中奇遇记》

yingyinNormal.en: One day, the legend will be born.
You had a partner? Yeah. When the legend becomes fact, you print the legend.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你曾经还有搭档？是的，当传奇变为现实的时候，你将铭刻传奇。

yingyinNormal.en: Your brother, the demigod, a super soldier, a living legend who kind of lives up to the legend.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的兄弟，那个小帅哥，超级英雄，一个不死的不负盛名的传奇。

yingyinNormal.en: Songs will be sung, tales will be told and Thorin Oakenshield will pass into legend.
yingyinNormal.zh: 尽情欢唱，歌功颂德，而索林·橡木盾会成为传奇。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies》

yingyinNormal.en: Really? On my planet, there's a legend about people like you. It's called Footloose.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真的吗？地球上有一则关于你这种人的传奇，"浑身是劲"。

yingyinNormal.en: She's a legend. She broke the all-time Scare Record with the scream in that very can!
yingyinNormal.zh: 她是传奇人物，她打破尖叫罐的空前惊吓纪录。

yingyinNormal.en: Bob, who appears to be a bald jaundice child, has pulled the famed sword right from its stone which legend dictates, makes him the new king.
yingyinNormal.zh: 鲍勃，这个一个光头的熊孩子，但他拔出了石中剑这一壮举，使他成功成为了新任国王。

yingyinNormal.en: That place is a legend. They make the most powerful, horrific weapons to ever torment the universe. I would very much like to go there, please.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那地方是个传奇。他们能造出最强大，最可怕的武器来折腾整个宇宙。我可是非常愿意去的。

yingyinNormal.en: But if you march back in there and you own it, you let those people know that you're better than them, and you will be a legend. Okay. Yeah. Okay?
yingyinNormal.zh: 但如果你昂首阔步回到派对上，不以为耻反以为荣，你让那些乌合之众明白你比他们强，你就会是传奇人物了。好。没错。好？
